<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: auto;
            width: 80%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .container_logo {
            width: 100% ;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container img {
            object-fit: contain;
            height: auto ;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            max-height: 180px ;
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #016D58;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px dashed #016D58;
            display: inline-block;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #016D58;
        }
        .ignore {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="container_logo">
            <img src="https://toolbox.lau.edu.lb/_ui/lau-logo-social-media.jpg" alt="LAU logo" /> 
        </div>

        <p>Hey <span class="highlight">{{ name }}</span> Club,</p>
        <p>Here's your 6-digit verification code ðŸ‘‡</p>
        <p class="code">{{ code }}</p>
        <p>Please enter this code in the app to confirm your email address.</p>

        <p class="ignore">If you did not request this email you can safely ignore it.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our App!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
